snippet.title: Baby Steps | Devolver Holiday Special Spotlight
snippet.description:
The creators of Baby Steps (who also happen to be the creators of QWOP, Getting Over It and Ape Out), show how they are working together to make their new game. 

https://www.babystepsgame.com/

Stepping onto PC and PlayStation 5 in 2024
